data.description: You'll fall in love with this beautiful Lindahl Cedar home nestled in secluded Larsmont hillside setting, with easy access to Hwy 61 Expressway. Majestic vaulted ceilings in the living room, open to main floor living areas and expansive deck with Lake Superior views (platform was originally constructed for a hot tub). Two bedrooms and a full bath complete the main level. The upper level loft/primary bedroom has an additional bath and walk-in closet and gorgeous lake views. The finished walk-out lower level makes nice use of flexible living space with a family room, additional bedroom/den, fitness area, laundry, hobby and storage rooms. Abundant storage throughout the home and the heated and insulated 2+ car detached garage. Immaculate home has been well maintained throughout!
